---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ChatWidget from '../components/ChatWidget.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Chat" description="Ask questions about Mnehmos's projects, architecture decisions, and technical implementations using an AI-powered chat interface.">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-copper/10 text-copper rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          RAG-Powered Chat
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">
          Ask About My Work
        </h1>
        <p class="text-stone-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Chat with an AI assistant that has indexed knowledge of all my projects, 
          architecture decisions, code patterns, and technical documentation.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Chat Widget (Standalone Mode) -->
      <ChatWidget standalone={true} />
      
      <!-- Info Cards -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-200">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-copper/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-1">Source Citations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
            Responses include [numbered] citations. Click to view the original source chunk.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-200">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-copper/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-1">Real-Time Streaming</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
            Responses stream in real-time using Server-Sent Events (SSE).
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-200">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-copper/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-1">Index Foundry</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
            Powered by my own RAG server built with Index Foundry MCP.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Example Questions -->
      <div class="mt-8 bg-stone-100 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">Example Questions</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">MCP Infrastructure</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-stone-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• What MCP servers have you built?</li>
              <li>• How does OODA MCP implement desktop control?</li>
              <li>• What's the architecture of Index Foundry?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Multi-Agent Systems</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-stone-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• How does the multi-agent framework work?</li>
              <li>• What is the Red→Green→Blue TDD workflow?</li>
              <li>• What role contracts exist in the framework?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Games</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-stone-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• How does the D&D 5e engine handle combat?</li>
              <li>• What tools are available for AI Dungeon Masters?</li>
              <li>• How are spell effects and conditions tracked?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Technical Details</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-stone-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• What design principles guide your MCP servers?</li>
              <li>• How is testing handled across projects?</li>
              <li>• What deployment strategies do you use?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
